Changes from the original hashicon:
- Rewritten renderer to output SVG strings instead of HTML Canvas
- Added Cardano bech32 address decoding (addr1, stake1, addr_test1, stake_test1)
- Removed external dependencies (@stablelib/blake2s, js-sha3)
- Uses credential hashes from Cardano addresses directly instead of re-hashing
- Added fallback hash (cyrb128) for arbitrary string inputs
- Dual ESM/CJS package with TypeScript declarations
